<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ع وض:</span> <span class="c2">(الْعِوَضُ)</span> وَاحِدُ <span class="c2">(الْأَعْوَاضِ)</span> .<span class="c5"> تَقُولُ مِنْهُ:</span> <span class="c2">(عَاضَهُ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(أَعَاضَهُ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(عَوَّضَهُ)</span> <span class="c2">(تَعْوِيضًا)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(عَاوَضَهُ)</span> أَيْ أَعْطَاهُ الْعِوَضَ. وَ <span class="c2">(اعْتَاضَ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(تَعَوَّضَ)</span> أَخَذَ الْعِوَضَ. وَ <span class="c2">(اسْتَعَاضَ)</span> أَيْ طَلَبَ الْعِوَضَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>